## Installation

```bash
$ npm install duo-canvas

```
## feature
#### 1. Welcome && Goodbye
```js
const cduo = require("duo-canvas");
const fs = require('fs');

const image = await new cduo.Welcome() // Goodbye()
    .setAvatar("https://i.ibb.co/VVf210d/W.jpg")
    .setUsername("W sarkaz")
    .setBg("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRxpRpPJqAaE3pdxIC0CbdeII1pyt2JUCVPdA&usqp=CAU")
    .setId("404")
    .toBuild();
    
  data = image.toBuffer();
  await fs.writeFileSync('./tmp/welcome.png', data)
 

```
<img src="data:image/png;base64," height="110"></img>

#### 2. Rank

```js
const cduo = require("duo-canvas");
const fs = require('fs');

const image = await new cduo.Rank()
    .setAvatar("https://i.ibb.co/VVf210d/W.jpg")
    .setBg("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRxpRpPJqAaE3pdxIC0CbdeII1pyt2JUCVPdA&usqp=CAU")
    .setNeedxp("100")
    .setCurrxp("55")
    .setLevel("7")
    .setColor("#3d4e7b")
    .toBuild();
    
  data = image.toBuffer();
  await fs.writeFileSync('./tmp/rank.png', data)
 
 
```
